.TH Lang_dir
.SH NAME
lang \- directory with translation data
.SH DESCRIPTION
.b Lang directory
Lang directory stores \[char46]lang files in subdirectories, each for different language.
.br
For example, all \[char46]lang files for english language must be placed in: lang/english
.br
Following lang directories are handled by engine:
.nf
data/lang
data/modules/[module]/lang
data/modules/[module]/chapters/[chapter]/lang
.SH FILES & SUBDIRECTORIES
Only *\[char46]lang files are handled inside lang directory.
.SH EXAMPLE
.nf
/lang
	items.lang
	dialogs.lang
	quests.lang
.SH SEE ALSO
files/.lang